text: Haemulon album, the white margate, is a species of ray-finned fish in the family Haemulidae native to the western Atlantic Ocean.Haemulon album (Grey Grunt, Grunt, Margaret Fish, Margaret Grunt, Margate, Margate Fish, Ronco Blanco, Viuda, White Grunt, White Margate, White Pogret, Yellow Grunt) ==References== ==External links== * Category:Haemulidae Category:Fish of the Caribbean Category:Fish described in 1830
